snippet.title: Fire Emblem Engage Expansion Pass – Fell Xenologue trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Buy now: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-games/Fire-Emblem-Engage-2267157.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=FireEmblemEngage%7CExpansionPass4AN%7Cm_id_pa2GZtBm5Q%7C2267157#Expansion_Pass

Fight alongside new allies and old foes to quell a rising darkness in Fell Xenologue! Dive into this new story in Pack 4 of the Fire Emblem Engage Expansion Pass, arriving April 5th.
